{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, chatbots have been employed to mediate consensus-building conversations (Shin et al., 2022).",
    "Moreover, numerous studies have focused on the development (Ahmed, 2019) and evaluation (Tavanapour and Bittner, 2018; Hwang and Won, 2021) of chatbots for ideation tasks.",
    "Chatbots have also been utilized to facilitate design thinking through the empathy map method (Bittner and Shoury, 2019).",
    "An intriguing example is CharacterChat, a chatbot designed to assist writers in creating fictional characters (Schmitt and Buschek, 2021).",
    "However, to the best of the authors' knowledge, no studies have specifically examined the use of chatbots in urban design tasks."
  ]
}